# Create a Device Configuration Policy called "OneDrive Known Folders"
# Description "Move users known folders to OneDrive silently and sign the user in silently. https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/windows/win32/shell/knownfolderid"
# Click Create
# Open the policy and select Settings
# Search for OneDrive, it can take time before the search works on a new policy
#
# Enable the 2 settings
# Silently sign in users to the OneDrive sync client with their Windows credentials
# Silently move Windows known folders to OneDrive
# to find the Tenant ID https://o365hq.com/faq/how-to-find-your-office-365-tenant-id